config VIDEO_OV9281
	tristate "OmniVision OV9281 sensor support"
	depends on I2C && VIDEO_DEV
	select MEDIA_CONTROLLER
	select VIDEO_V4L2_SUBDEV_API
	select V4L2_FWNODE
	help
	  This is a V4L2 sensor driver for the OmniVision OV9281
	  global shutter camera sensor.

	  The OV9281 is a 1MP (1280x800) monochrome global shutter
	  sensor with MIPI CSI-2 interface, commonly used for
	  machine vision and depth sensing applications.

	  Supports external trigger mode via FSIN pin for
	  multi-camera synchronization.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
	  module will be called ov9281.
